**RESP2:**

[Array reply](../../develop/reference/protocol-spec#arrays): a list of elements in the specified range, or an empty array if the key doesn't exist.

**RESP3:**

[Array reply](../../develop/reference/protocol-spec#arrays): a list of elements in the specified range, or an empty array if the key doesn't exist.

